quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth will be convulsed with a convulsion
  99,2,and the earth brought out its ladings
  99,3,"and the human being said: What is with it"
  99,4,On that Day it will divulge its news
  99,5,for your Lord revealed it
  99,6,"On that Day humanity will issue, separately, that they may be caused to see their actions"
  99,7,And whoever does the weight of an atom of good will see it
  99,8,And whoever does the weight of an atom of the worst will see it